/* ==========================================
   TOM TALK TOPICS — WORKING DONE PHASE, LEVEL 1
   phase === "working.done" && friendshipLevel === 1

   CHARACTER: Tom Reese, Clerk at Ruby's Diner
   → Friendly, encouraging, happy for you.
   → Congratulates you on making it through the shift.
   → Warm older-brother vibes.

   WORKING DONE L1 TONE:
   → Player has finished their 8 hours and is leaving.
   → Tom is proud of them for surviving another shift.

   CONTEXTS:
   dinerRubys_workingDone_morning
   dinerRubys_workingDone_afternoon
   dinerRubys_workingDone_evening
========================================== */

